OL,6,FWorkington Town's rugby league player
OL,7,FTom Curwen has been banned from sport
OL,8,Ffor 18 months for breaching anti-
OL,9,Fdoping rules.
OL,11,FCurwen broke the anti-doping rules for
OL,12,Fthe presence and use of a prohibited
OL,13,Fsubstance.
OL,15,FCurwen's sample tested positive for
OL,16,Famphetamine following an in-
OL,17,Fcompetition test.
