OL,6,FThe UKAD (UK Anti-Doping) Organisation
OL,7,Fnotified Curwen that he may have
OL,8,Fcommitted Anti-Doping Rule Violations
OL,9,F(ADRV).
OL,11,FIn response, Curwen provided evidence
OL,12,Fto show that he suffers from ADHD and
OL,13,Fused the substances to treat his
OL,14,Fcondition.
OL,16,FCurwen was required to apply for
OL,17,FNational Therapeutic Use Exemption in
OL,18,Fadvance of taking an amphetamine but
OL,19,Fhe did not do so.
